<p>Split between the global media capital of the world and the fastest growing fintech hub in Europe, Wachsman PR services some of the most disruptive and influential forces in fintech. Founded in December 2015 by David Wachsman, the agency has become leaders in generating media exposure and brand recognition for companies in the blockchain, cryptocurrency, equity crowdfunding, alternative asset, and real estate investment industries. With clients around the globe and teams working from New York City and Dublin, Wachsman PR has established a peerless reputation in the space.</p>